  <summary>5/19/1988--Introduced.
Nuclear Decommissioning Reserve Fund Act of 1988 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) decrease from 34 percent to 15 percent the rate of the tax imposed on the income of any Nuclear Decommissioning Reserve Fund; and (2) remove restrictions on permitted investments of Fund monies.</summary>
